text: Bukit Brown MRT Station (CC18) is a Circle MRT Line station in Singapore. The station has never been used. It was built for future use. Nearby is Bukit Brown Cemetery, the only remaining cemetery in Singapore. ==Following Stations== Previous: Caldecott (CC17) Next: Botanic Gardens (CC19/DT9) ==Related pages== *Mass Rapid Transit (Singapore) Category:Mass Rapid Transit (Singapore) stations
